Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said this again and again,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's really no reason to get \Nserialized while you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is doing it, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's working by himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but with two conditions.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.62,0:00:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditions?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.49,0:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One, you submit this as a one-shot for the \Nnext "Golden Future Cup" and it does well.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Golden Future Cup?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in the summer, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing before that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.21,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to bring me a 19 page \Nstory for this series every two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a rehearsal for actual serialization?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.64,0:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you usually do this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how I want to do it this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.15,0:00:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do this much, there's no way \Nyou can do it while still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.11,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you guys are not Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And writing a detective manga is completely \Ndifferent than writing a battle manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.37,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you don't get this serialized, \Nit will be a good experience for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely show you we can do this
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and then get serialized for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have lost to you guys in "Next,"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll beat you for sure this time, Ashirogi Muto.
