Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.74,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so far been successful in a variety of fields.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting, writing, fashion design.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.19,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to express myself in \Nways other than just music.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That desire has not dwindled.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It still burns brightly even now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it continues to get stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's overflowing and \Nthere's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I wish to tell you tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you listen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a magnificent concert.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives me pride as your producer.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.50,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Koogy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyde.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting here for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.80,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be sure to come back successful.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Uchida.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an editor at Yueisha.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.11,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen today's paper?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N—No, not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to read it now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV's fine too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, if you're planning on becoming a mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then at least glance through the \Npaper first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.41,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,First thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You just woke me up—
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.83,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\fad(100,0)\blur0.869} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.83,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(767.333,488.687)\frz0.7\fad(100,0)\blur0.869\bord1.136\c&HCECBCB&\3c&HCECBCB&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.83,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\fad(100,0)\blur4.68\bord2.674\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I wish to tell you tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you listen?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.92,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\blur0.869} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.92,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(767.333,488.687)\frz0.7\blur0.869\bord1.136\c&HCECBCB&\3c&HCECBCB&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.92,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\blur4.68\bord2.674\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.38,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After this concert, I will be \Ntaking a break from music.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.72,0:20:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, Makaino Koji, will become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Makaino Koji?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.68,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "Colorfusical's" writer is the singer Koogy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing dirty.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be in Jack's
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.69,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,"Golden Future Cup" contest this summer
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning to get his fans to fill out the questionnaire for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pissed off.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,and continue to broaden my horizons.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about going to the office and protesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I look forward to your support!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.70,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\blur0.869} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.70,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(767.333,488.687)\frz0.7\blur0.869\bord1.136\c&HCECBCB&\3c&HCECBCB&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.70,TVAnnouncement,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.667,488.019)\frz0.7\blur4.68\bord2.674\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&} Announces Sudden Hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai said he'd go too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine going on my own, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys should come too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.54,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai said that you two are in \Nthe "Golden Future Cup" as well,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I should at least mention it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to come?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have school today.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What time can you come?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're coming, we can wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to Takagi about it first.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know by this afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.90,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing of his announcement is a cheap trick.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his fans'll definitely fill \Nout the questionnaire for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner of the "Golden Future Cup" would \Nbe in the best position for getting serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to get first, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you should have waited
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,until you're serialized to \Nmake a public announcement?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna tell the world, now's the best time.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.01,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That way my fans will all vote for \Nme on those questionnaire thingies.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll be that easy—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My drawings are this good.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.69,0:22:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll succeed in a multitude of \Nmediums and become a true star.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's here then, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let Koogy get away with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they consent to something like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll teach the editing department a thing or two.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.01,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Fukuda,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.05,0:22:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}We're now proceeding en route
